Error: Error: "Unable To Start The Server. Error 1006: Connection Refused"

Solution: Step 1: Check server status
- Go to your Pterodactyl panel and check if your server is running or stopped.
- If the server is stopped, try starting it again to see if the error resolves.

Step 2: Check firewall settings
- Login to your server and check if the firewall settings allow connections to the server.
- You can use the following command on Linux
